Clinical Standards
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Segment nomenclature, parameter definitions, and reflux thresholds follow:

- IAC Vascular Testing Standards (Intersocietal Accreditation Commission)
- SVU Professional Performance Guidelines: Lower Extremity Venous Duplex
  (Society for Vascular Ultrasound)
- AIUM/ACR/SPR/SRU Practice Parameter for Peripheral Venous Ultrasound
- CEAP 2020 classification (Journal of Vascular Surgery: Venous and
  Lymphatic Disorders)
- ESVS 2022 Clinical Practice Guidelines on Venous Thrombosis
  (European Society for Vascular Surgery)

LOINC codes (Regenstrief Institute) and SNOMED CT codes (SNOMED
International) used as references are property of their respective owners.
